high_descs: Turn left and walk up to a sidetable that is in front of you across the room.
Pick up a bread from the sidetable.
Turn around and walk to a microwave which is on your left.
Put the bread inside the microwave.
Go back to the sidetable.
Pick up a butterknife from the sidetable.
Now go back to the microwave.
Cut the bread in the microwave using the butterknife.
anns.task_desc: Using the butterknife, cut the bread inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight to reach the side table
Take a bread from the side table
Turn back and take few steps and turn left to reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the bread loaf inside of it and close the oven
Turn back and turn right to reach the side table again
Take a knife from the top of the side table
Turn back and take few steps and turn left to reach the microwave oven again
Open the oven and cut the bread loaf which is kept inside and close the oven
anns.task_desc: Cut the bread loaf in the microwave oven

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the side table.
Pick up bread from the desk.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the microwave.
Place bread on the microwave.
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near side table.
Pick up bread from the desk.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the microwave.
Place bread on the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Collecting bread from different places and arranging them on a microwave.
